{"tid":1478726,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"全世界同我入黎幫手！力保廣東話！","createTime":"2019-08-16T15:36:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T15:45:24.000Z","uid":145863,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b81b509aa6e4147f52e23f78ee2b200569f9b328","tid":1478726,"uid":145863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:36:53.000Z","msg":"【嚴防滅絕廣東話！】<br />\n<br />\nPK政府想靜雞雞刪去中文聆聽及/說話卷，話其中一個原因是學生壓力太大。但教育局從不反思學生學習壓力太大的根源是整個教育制度的問題。應該係想幫內地生爭學位。此舉唔洗問阿貴都知係想幫內地生爭學位啦！<br />\n<br />\n以下係諮詢文件：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/about-edb/press/consultation/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edb.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fabout-edb%2Fpress%2Fconsultation%2F&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0aWONrq76Y1XZ%2F%2BBeLOBzgc%3D&h=05127dfc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/about-edb/press/consultation/</a><br />\n<br />\n如果唔同意，請於二零一九年九月十六日（星期一）或之前，以郵寄、電郵或傳真方式把書面意見交予專責小組秘書處：<br />\n<br />\n郵寄地址： 香港灣仔<br />\n皇后大道東 213 號<br />\n胡忠大廈 13 樓 1301 室<br />\n學校課程檢討專責小組秘書處<br />\n<br />\n電郵： taskforce_cur@edb.gov.hk<br />\n<br />\n傳真號碼： (852) 2573 5299」<br />\n<br />\n「遞交意見書時是否提供個人資料，並無硬性規定。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n【Template of letter】<br />\n<br />\n電郵標題請自行撰寫<br />\n<br />\n致專責小組成員：<br />\n<br />\n本人為香港市民，有聞 貴組於6月28日文件中提出刪去文憑試聆聽及說話考卷，本人堅表強烈反對，原因如下：<br />\n<br />\n一，掌握母語不等於能以母語表達，說話要言之有物、出口成文，除了要豐富的詞彙，亦要有清晰的表達方式，說話卷的核心價值在於檢視學生在日常用語之外，能否有效建構論點展開討論，而廢除後則無地方訓練學生這項基本能力。<br />\n<br />\n二，掌握母語不等於能理解別人話語內容，聆聽別人的說話可以訓練學生將對話精煉的能力，亦即是捕捉重點的能力，假如廢除，恐怕學生會失去一個練習的平台，無法與人有效溝通。<br />\n<br />\n三，以語言系公開試ielts雅思為例，考核學生英語水平以讀聽寫說四考卷，尤其是以說話難度最高，一向是該考試衡量英語高水平者的好標準，如今 貴組研廢除聆、說二卷，猶如自斷一臂。<br />\n<br />\n綜合以上及眾多學者之言，冀 貴組於此項教育改革方向予於重新考慮。<br />\n<br />\n此致<br />\n<br />\n香港市民<br />\n<br />\n#廢中已交功課 #大家做嘢 #send個電郵舉手之勞 #嚴防滅絕廣東話"},{"pid":"1e2e7c6a943ba0baa22982305ef91cafba1d2571","tid":1478726,"uid":145863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:37:12.000Z","msg":"自推10"},{"pid":"bcf382d4aa9499b7c54c6645e159f56ecc1cba03","tid":1478726,"uid":145863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:37:22.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"b88883abd5be713abebc0c7a929f408c89b90772","tid":1478726,"uid":145863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:37:33.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"493b186f4706aa9254fec1760f7b60721527a9c5","tid":1478726,"uid":145863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:37:51.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"e592f78aaa60c76920bf9bfe47997adec8cff91c","tid":1478726,"uid":145863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:38:01.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"fc4ae2c895f8d6811b15b544e86fe9aa75fff3cc","tid":1478726,"uid":145863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:38:15.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"227affab38386fd4de4b203feb0cb05ae77c28a3","tid":1478726,"uid":145863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:38:25.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"d34276b8364cfb2c892e2b29fd80684b354d2287","tid":1478726,"uid":145863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:38:35.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"74c53c9cb23613c9f0c55e054df9868ec13013ac","tid":1478726,"uid":145863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:38:46.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"8039a3f367a490c617b8ef221d8bc9926f43d2dd","tid":1478726,"uid":145863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:38:56.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"c31de9d64190965f7f88caa3c237a2926f582cee","tid":1478726,"uid":145863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:39:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b1d81e9657f70858eae0bd9772accb6815f8971","tid":1478726,"uid":145863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:41:33.000